<add><ab facs="#facs_97_line_1573121162470_774">etc </ab></add> das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r1l5"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> / vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> darümb <expan>Jacob<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r1l6">Topler vnd etlich <expan>ande<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> die das antrifft für vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r1l7">beſant vnd cʒurede geſäcʒt . die <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vns <expan>geantvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> . Sie </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r1l8">dunk vnbillich vnd fremde ſein . daʒ ſie von Jn ſchuld </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r1l9">vorder . oder daʒ ſie ſölch brief ynnehab . <expan>vvan<ex>n</ex></expan> ſie darümb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r1l10">niht vviſſen . darcʒu ſeẏ dy <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan> Sele vnd <expan>han<ex>n</ex>s</expan> Topler </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r1l11">Jr wirt <expan>ſelıg<ex>en</ex></expan> manig Jar hie cʒu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> vnd anderſwo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r1l12">beẏ Jn geſeſſen in <expan>gute<ex>m</ex></expan> gerichte . vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>dhein<ex>er</ex>leẏ</expan> ſchuld </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r1l13">an ſie nye geuordert weder mit reht noch on recht / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r1l14">Aber wie darümb het die <expan>vorgen<ex>ante</ex></expan> Sele cʒu <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r1l15">Jacob oder <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> burgern icht <expan>cʒeſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . darümb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r1l16">vvöllen vvir 
<del rend="strikethrough">Jn </del> Jr . oder irem Scheinboten mit irem <expan>volle<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r1l17">gewalte <expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>cʒogens</expan> ſleunigs rehten gern helffen . <expan>vven<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r1l18">vvir des ermand werden So dy <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> cʒu <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> ſıe <expan>cʒeſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r1l19">het anheim ſind . <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> wo vvir <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>gnedige<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r1l20"><expan>h<ex>e</ex>rcʒog</expan> <expan>Otte<ex>n</ex></expan> . vnd auch <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb vnd dinſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r1l21">beweıſen <expan>möhte<ex>n</ex></expan> . Des <expan>w<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vvir wıllig vnd <expan>tete<ex>n</ex></expan> das <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> . </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r1l22"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vj̃ poſt valentini Anno etc xx<hi rend="sup">o</hi></ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_97" id="47v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Petern von <expan>Stetemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>,
                            <expan>amptman<ex>n</ex></expan> czu Lauden </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> von <expan>Stetemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, als
                        ir uns <expan>geschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von Selen
                                <expan>Toplerin<ex>n</ex></expan>, <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>burgerin<ex>n</ex></expan> czu Lauden wegen <add>etc.</add>, das
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> und <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        darümb <expan>Jacob<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Topler und etlich
                                <expan>ande<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan>, die das antrifft, für uns besant und czurede
                        gesäczt. Die <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns
                            <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>, sie dunk unbillich und fremde sein,
                        daz sie von in schuld vorder oder daz sie sölch brief ynnehab,
                                <expan>wan<ex>n</ex></expan> sie darümb niht wissen. Darczu sey dy
                                <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan> Sele und
                            <expan>Han<ex>n</ex>s</expan> Topler ir wirt
                            <expan>selig<ex>en</ex></expan> manig jar hie czu
                                <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> und anderswo bey in gesessen in
                                <expan>gute<ex>m</ex></expan> gerichte und
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dhein<ex>er</ex>ley</expan> schuld an sie nye gevordert weder mit
                        reht noch on recht. Aber wie darümb het die
                            <expan>vorgen<ex>ante</ex></expan> Sele czu <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> Jacob oder <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> burgern icht <expan>cze
                            sprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, darümb wöllen wir ir oder irem scheinboten
                        mit irem <expan>volle<ex>m</ex></expan> gewalte
                            <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czogens</expan> sleunigs rehten gern helffen,
                                <expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan> wir des ermand werden, so dy
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, czu <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> sie
                            <expan>cze sprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> het, anheim sind.
                                <expan>Dan<ex>n</ex></expan> wo wir <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedige<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>h<ex>e</ex>rczog</expan>
<expan>Otte<ex>n</ex></expan>, und auch <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb und dinst beweisen
                                <expan>möhte<ex>n</ex></expan>. Des <expan>w<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wir
                        willig und <expan>tete<ex>n</ex></expan> das <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vi post Valentini anno etc. xx<hi rend="sup">o</hi>.</ab>
</div>
